Interface Name<IN,OUT>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    From<IN,OUT>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EMBuilder

    public interface Name<IN,OUT>
extends From<IN,OUT>
    First (optional) step of the builder that allow too set a name to the ElementMapper.
    This step is optional.
    Next optional steps: DefaultInput, Transformer, DefaultOutput.
    Next mandatory steps: From, To.
    Author:
    eschoysman
    See Also:
    ClassMapper.addMapping(), EMBuilder.using(Mapper,ClassMapper), ElementMapper, builder package
